                </did>
                <scopecontent id="ref65">
                    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                    <p>A letter from Oxman in 1976 to the principal of Erasmus Hall in 2076, with correspondence from alumni, and a 1981 thank-you note from President Ronald Reagan.</p>
                </scopecontent>
                <c id="ref52" level="file">
                    <did>
                        <unittitle>"To the Principal of Erasmus Hall High School in 2076"</unittitle>
