                        <container parent="cid3917002" type="Folder">10</container>
                        <unitdate>1976 December</unitdate>
                    </did>
                    <scopecontent id="ref61">
                        <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                        <p>A letter written by Harriet Oxman, principal of Erasmus Hall in 1976, to the person holding her position a century hence. A copy was placed in a time capsule on the campus grounds. The letter is reproduced in Oxman's 
                            <emph render="italic">The Rise and Fall, Erasmus Hall High School</emph> (2017), pp. 61-66 (folders 25-26).</p>
                    </scopecontent>
                </c>
